summary:
Abandoned House in Winterhold with some beautiful changes around plus more to come later on.
Work in progress - early release.
descriptionHtml:
If you got any ideas on what I could do, feel free to share in the comment field! It\'s all work in progress with my updates at this point. I\'ll perhaps update more often as to give you people a chance to perhaps guide some of my choices into a direction you would like to see.

Winterhold Lore-friendly Changes
Work in progress - early release.

--- I got two projects this and Abandoned Wine Cellar (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27622) so not sure which one to dedicate my time on, so please give any feedback if you have an opinion about this mod! I really like to hear it, even if it\'s bad! ---

v0.2
- Added Abaonded Wine Cellar in The Frozen Hearth cellar. It\'s been a long time since anyone visited that wine cellar, pretty much all forgotten now.
- Few tweaks around Abandoned House.

v0.1
- Added Abandoned House in Winterhold
- Changes done to landscape underneath the Abandoned House
- Added medium bonefire to Winterhold, beautiful to watch
- Added tree\\\'s and bushes, etc around the Abandoned House.
author: ValenwoodElf aka Sparrow
